This documents explains the use cases which have been run to generate the log files

Physical Setup
==============
                   Va
                   |
              |    |
Vb --- Rb ----|----Ra --- Ta
       |      |
       |
       Tb

Vb - Viewer in hospital B
Rb - Archiver/Relay in hospital B
Tb - Tx in hospital B

Ra - Archiver/Relay in hospital A
Ta - Tx in hospital A


StreamFilterTable
=================

Src	Dest	Relay
---	---	----

Ta	ALL	Ra
Ta	Ra	-
Ra	Va	-

ALL	Rb	Ra
ALL	Vb	Rb
Rb	Vb	-

Tb	ALL	Rb
Tb	Rb	-

(Tb	Vb	--) Optional Direct


UseCases
=======

1. relay_pvr : PVR on Ra

	Vb --- Rb ---|--- Ra --- Ta

2. relay_record : Record on Ra

	Vb --- Rb ---|--- Ra --- Ta

3. relay_playback : Playback from Ra

	Vb --- Rb ---|--- Ra

4. playback : Playback from Ra

               Va
               |
               |
	       Ra 

5. TBD: pvr : PVR on Rb

	Vb --- Rb 
	       |
	       |
	       Tb

LogFiles
=======

In the log files the following JIDs are used

Ta - deviceuser-relaypvr
Ra - srcrelay-relaypvr
Rb - destrelay-relaypvr
Vb/Va - roomuser-relaypvr

Testing room UI without Admin UI or Tx
======================================

To test room UI without admin UI do the following

1. run the TestApplet
2. runtest ... room_test_<option>_admin_setup.exp (Ask Padmaja if you have questions about option)
3. run the TestApplet
4. runtest ... device_srcrelay_destrelay_user.exp (This will simulate the Tx, srcrelay, destrelay)
5. Bring up the room UI
